618
00:34:46,293 --> 00:34:47,752
Murray Hill.

619
00:34:47,836 --> 00:34:50,713
I can waIk to the office, but I don't.

620
00:34:50,797 --> 00:34:53,966
I wonder if you're gonna get a call.

