628
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:15,988
What about writing?

629
00:35:16,072 --> 00:35:17,573
That's just for fun.

630
00:35:19,034 --> 00:35:20,659
It's your hobby.

631
00:35:30,462 --> 00:35:31,420
I should go.

632
