635
00:35:57,197 --> 00:35:59,865
I can wrap up a piece of pie for you.

636
00:35:59,950 --> 00:36:03,035
- It's pine nuts and pineapple.
- If I eat any more,

637
00:36:03,119 --> 00:36:05,037
