797
00:45:35,566 --> 00:45:36,942
What did you get?

798
00:45:37,026 --> 00:45:38,610
Bobbie?

799
00:45:38,694 --> 00:45:40,612
Lots of people have had that.

800
00:45:40,696 --> 00:45:42,489
Excuse me?

801
00:45:42,573 --> 00:45:44,866
Please. I laugh at you.

802
00:45:44,951 --> 00:45:48,078
